headline: 'Risk-On' Investor Attitude Could Drag U.S. Utility Stock Performance In 2025
summary: Since the election, the S&P 500 Utilities index has underperformed the S&P 500, declining just over 1% as of the Dec. 11 close compared to the S&P 500's 5% gain.
